<div class="opaqueback">
<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="section-header text-center center">
<h2 id="request">Internships</h2>
</div>
<div class="col-md-5"><center><img alt="Internships" class="img-responsive" src="images/home/sb-puzzle.png" style="border-radius: 0;" width="325" /></center></div>
<div class="col-md-7" style="margin-top: -20px;">
<p class="text-center"><strong>Enhance your learning goals with an internship!</strong></p>
<p class="arssb-internships fadeInUp wow">Get real-world work experience through hands-on learning supervised by professionals in your field. Schedule a meeting with our Student Advisors, learn about opportunities available to you or let us help you to reach out to the community and seek the opportunity you're looking for.</p>
<p class="text-center"><strong>Ready to take your learning to the next level?</strong></p>
<div class="btn-group" style="min-width: 95%;"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-haspopup="true" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#" type="button"> ARSSB Student Advising <span class="caret"></span> </a>
